ApplicationSubmissionInfoGrp.FormAndInfoAndMaterialsTxt: THE FOUNDATION DOES NOT REQUIRE A SPECIFIC APPLICATION FORMAT OR ANY PARTICULAR MATERIALS OTHER THAN AN EXPLANATION FOR THE PURPOSE OF THE PROPOSED GRANT AND A COPY OF THE PROPOSED GRANTEE'S IRS TAX EXEMPTION LETTER.
ApplicationSubmissionInfoGrp.SubmissionDeadlinesTxt: ALL APPLICATIONS SHOULD BE SUBMITTED IN WRITING ON OR BEFORE OCTOBER 31ST OF EACH CALENDAR YEAR
ApplicationSubmissionInfoGrp.RestrictionsOnAwardsTxt: NO RESTRICTIONS OR LIMITATIONS ARE PLACED ON GRANTS OTHER THAN THAT WHICH IS REQUIRED TO MANTAIN THE FOUNDATION'S IRS APPROVED TAX EXEMPT STATUS
